        <div style="font-size:90%;">Standard of Cyrus the Great</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><figure-inline class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:Image/Frameless" data-mw='{"caption":"The Achaemenid Empire at its greatest territorial extent,&lt;br data-parsoid=&apos;{\"stx\":\"html\",\"selfClose\":true}&apos;/> under the rule of &lt;a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"./Darius_I\" title=\"Darius I\" data-parsoid=&apos;{\"stx\":\"simple\",\"a\":{\"href\":\"./Darius_I\"},\"sa\":{\"href\":\"Darius I\"}}&apos;>Darius I&lt;/a> (522 BC to 486 BC)"}'><a href="./File:Achaemenid_Empire_(flat_map).svg"><img resource="./File:Achaemenid_Empire_(flat_map).svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/Achaemenid_Empire_%28flat_map%29.svg/250px-Achaemenid_Empire_%28flat_map%29.svg.png" data-file-width="672" data-file-height="442" data-file-type="drawing" height="164" width="250" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/Achaemenid_Empire_%28flat_map%29.svg/500px-Achaemenid_Empire_%28flat_map%29.svg.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/Achaemenid_Empire_%28flat_map%29.svg/375px-Achaemenid_Empire_%28flat_map%29.svg.png 1.5x"/></a></figure-inline><div style="font-size:90%;position:relative;top:0.3em;">The Achaemenid Empire at its greatest territorial extent,<br/> under the rule of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Darius_I" title="Darius I" class="mw-redirect">Darius I</a> (522 BC to 486 BC)</div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Capital</th><td><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Babylon" title="Babylon">Babylon</a><sup about="#mwt1155" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-EY_2-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"EY"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-EY-2"}}'><a href="./Achaemenid_Empire#cite_note-EY-2" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 2;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[2]</span></a></sup> (main capital), <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Pasargadae" title="Pasargadae">Pasargadae</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Ecbatana" title="Ecbatana">Ecbatana</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Susa" title="Susa">Susa</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Persepolis" title="Persepolis">Persepolis</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row">Common<span typeof="mw:Entity">Â </span>languages</th><td><div class="plainlist ">
