ieni</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Bithynia" title="Bithynia" id="mwA2c">Mariandyni</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Cappadocia" title="Cappadocia" id="mwA2g">Cappadocians</a>,<sup about="#mwt834" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-vii-72_127-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"vii-72"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-vii-72-127"}}'><a href="./Achaemenid_Empire#cite_note-vii-72-127" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 126;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[126]</span></a></sup> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Phrygia" title="Phrygia" id="mwA2k">Phrygians</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Armenia" title="Armenia" id="mwA2o">Armenians</a>,<sup about="#mwt836" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-vii-73_128-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"vii-73"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-vii-73-128"}}'><a href="./Achaemenid_Empire#cite_note-vii-73-128" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 127;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[127]</span></a></sup> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Lydia" title="Lydia" id="mwA2s">Lydians</a>, <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Mysia" title="Mysia" id="mwA2w">Mysians</a>,<sup about="#mwt838" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-vii-74_129-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"vii-74"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-vii-74-129"}}'><a href="./Achaemenid_Empire#cite_note-vii-74-129" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 128;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[128]</span></a></sup> Asian <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Bithyni" title="Bithyni" id="mwA20">Thracians</a>,<sup about="#mwt840" class="mw-ref" id="cite_ref-vii-75_130-0" rel="dc:references" typeof="mw:Extension/ref" data-mw='{"name":"ref","attrs":{"name":"vii-75"},"body":{"id":"mw-reference-text-cite_note-vii-75-130"}}'><a href="./Achaemenid_Empire#cite_note-vii-75-130" style="counter-reset: mw-Ref 129;"><span class="mw-reflink-text">[129]</span></a></sup> <a rel="mw:W