</section><section data-mw-section-id="28" id="mwBVI"><h3 id="Attested">Attested</h3>
<p id="mwBVM">There were 13 attested kings during the 220 years of the Achaemenid Empire's existence. The reign of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_II_of_Persia" title="Artaxerxes II of Persia" id="mwBVQ">Artaxerxes II</a> was the longest, lasting 47 years</p>
