<tr style="background:#cdcdcd;" id="mwBfg">
<td id="mwBfk"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Darius_I_of_Persia" title="Darius I of Persia" id="mwBfo" class="mw-redirect">Darius I the Great</a></td><td id="mwBfs">521â€“486</td><td id="mwBfw"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Atossa" title="Atossa" id="mwBf0">Atossa</a> <br id="mwBf4"/> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artystone" title="Artystone" id="mwBf8">Artystone</a> <br id="mwBgA"/> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Parmys" title="Parmys" id="mwBgE">Parmys</a> <br id="mwBgI"/> <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Phratagune" title="Phratagune" id="mwBgM" class="new">Phratagune</a></td><td id="mwBgQ">son-in-law of Cyrus the Great, son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Hystaspes_(father_of_Darius_I)" title="Hystaspes (father of Darius I)" id="mwBgU">Hystaspes</a>, grandson of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Arsames" title="Arsames" id="mwBgY">Arsames</a> <br id="mwBgc"/> Armies defeated at <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Battle_of_Marathon" title="Battle of Marathon" id="mwBgg">Battle of Marathon</a> in Greece.</td></tr>
<tr id="mwBgk">
<td id="mwBgo"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Xerxes_I_of_Persia" title="Xerxes I of Persia" id="mwBgs" class="mw-redirect">Xerxes I the Great</a></td><td id="mwBgw">485â€“465</td><td id="mwBg0"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Amestris" title="Amestris" id="mwBg4">Amestris</a></td><td id="mwBg8">son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Darius_I" title="Darius I" id="mwBhA" class="mw-redirect">Darius I</a> and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Atossa" title="Atossa" id="mwBhE">Atossa</a> <br id="mwBhI"/> Victorious at <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Battle_of_Thermopylae" title="Battle of Thermopylae" id="mwBhM">Battle of Thermopylae</a> <br id="mwBhQ"/> Defeated at <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Battle_of_Salamis" title="Battle of Salamis" id="mwBhU">Battle of Salamis</a></td></tr>
<tr style="background:#cdcdcd;" id="mwBhY">
<td id="mwBhc"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_I_of_Persia" title="Artaxerxes I of Persia" id="mwBhg">Artaxerxes I Longimanus</a></td><td id="mwBhk">465â€“424</td><td id="mwBho"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Damaspia" title="Damaspia" id="mwBhs">Damaspia</a> <br id="mwBhw"/> Cosmartidene <br id="mwBh0"/> Alogyne <br id="mwBh4"/> Andia</td><td id="mwBh8">son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Xerxes_I_of_Persia" title="Xerxes I of Persia" id="mwBiA" class="mw-redirect">Xerxes I</a> and Amestris</td></tr>
<tr id="mwBiE">
<td id="mwBiI"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Xerxes_II_of_Persia" title="Xerxes II of Persia" id="mwBiM">Xerxes II</a></td><td id="mwBiQ">424</td><td id="mwBiU"></td><td id="mwBiY">son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_I" title="Artaxerxes I" id="mwBic" class="mw-redirect">Artaxerxes I</a> and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Damaspia" title="Damaspia" id="mwBig">Damaspia</a></td></tr>
<tr style="background:#cdcdcd;" id="mwBik">
<td id="mwBio"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Sogdianus_of_Persia" title="Sogdianus of Persia" id="mwBis">Sogdianus</a></td><td id="mwBiw">424â€“423</td><td id="mwBi0"></td><td id="mwBi4">Son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_I" title="Artaxerxes I" id="mwBi8" class="mw-redirect">Artaxerxes I</a> and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Alogyne" title="Alogyne" id="mwBjA" class="new">Alogyne</a>; half-brother and rival of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Xerxes_II" title="Xerxes II" id="mwBjE" class="mw-redirect">Xerxes II</a></td></tr>
<tr id="mwBjI">
<td id="mwBjM"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Darius_II_of_Persia" title="Darius II of Persia" id="mwBjQ" class="mw-redirect">Darius II</a></td><td id="mwBjU">423â€“405</td><td id="mwBjY"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Parysatis" title="Parysatis" id="mwBjc">Parysatis</a></td><td id="mwBjg">Son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_I" title="Artaxerxes I" id="mwBjk" class="mw-redirect">Artaxerxes I</a> and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Cosmartidene" title="Cosmartidene" id="mwBjo" class="new">Cosmartidene</a>; half-brother and rival of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Xerxes_II" title="Xerxes II" id="mwBjs" class="mw-redirect">Xerxes II</a></td></tr>
<tr style="background:#cdcdcd;" id="mwBjw">
<td id="mwBj0"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_II_of_Persia" title="Artaxerxes II of Persia" id="mwBj4">Artaxerxes II Mnemon</a></td><td id="mwBj8">404â€“359</td><td id="mwBkA"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Stateira_(wife_of_Artaxerxes_II)" title="Stateira (wife of Artaxerxes II)" id="mwBkE">Stateira</a></td><td id="mwBkI">son of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Darius_II_of_Persia" title="Darius II of Persia" id="mwBkM" class="mw-redirect">Darius II</a> (see also <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Xenophon" title="Xenophon" id="mwBkQ">Xenophon</a>)</td></tr>
</tbody></table>

<p id="mwBkU">Early in the reign of Artaxerxes II, in 399 BC, the Persians lost control over Egypt. They regained control 57 years later, in 342 BC, when <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Artaxerxes_III" title="Artaxerxes III" id="mwBkY">Artaxerxes III</a> conquered Egypt.</p>

