Dw">Battle of the Eurymedon</a>.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-55" id="cite_note-55"><a href="./Achaemenid_Empire#cite_ref-55" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">â†‘ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-55" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt207" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://plutarch.classicauthors.net/PlutarchsLives/PlutarchsLives3.html"},"title":{"wt":"Plutarch&apos;s Lives by Plutarch: Themistocles Themistocles, Part II"},"last":{"wt":""},"first":{"wt":""},"date":{"wt":"2015-10-01"},"website":{"wt":""},"archive-url":{"wt":"https://web.archive.org/web/20151001032753/http://plutarch.classicauthors.net/PlutarchsLives/PlutarchsLives3.html"},"archive-date":{"wt":"2015-10-01"},"dead-url":{"wt":""},"access-date":{"wt":"2018-03-22"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCD0"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20151001032753/http://plutarch.classicauthors.net/PlutarchsLives/PlutarchsLives3.html" id="mwCD4">"Plutarch's Lives by Plutarch: Themistocles Themistocles, Part II"</a>. 2015-10-01. Archived from <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://plutarch.classicauthors.net/PlutarchsLives/PlutarchsLives3.html" id="mwCD8">the original</a> on 2015-10-01<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCEA">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCEE">2018-03-22</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Plutarch%27s+Lives+by+Plutarch%3A+Themistocles+Themistocles%2C+Part+II&amp;rft.date=2015-10-01&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fplutarch.classicauthors.net%2FPlutarchsLives%2FPlutarchsLives3.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAchaemenid+Empire" class="Z3988" about="#mwt207" id="mwCEI"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about=